 zweiten Nachkriegszeit resultierte. Diese Konvergenzen und Diskrepanzen, eingebettet in den europäischen Rahmen, bilden das übergreifende Thema des Bandes.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aHistoryxHistorical PeriodsxContemporary HistoryxContemporary History until 1945. 4aDeutschland. 4aFrankreich. 4aGeschichte 1871-1949. 4aNachkriegszeit. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh1 aAllain, Jean-Claude, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBariéty, Jacques, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBeatrix, Bouvier, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBokelmann, Elisabeth, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBroder, Albert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDedinger, Béatrice, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDefrance, Corine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFabréguet, Michel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFisch, Stefan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGandouly, Jaques, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGuillen, Pierre, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGuillen, Pierre, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGödde-Baumanns, Beate, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHau, Michel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKaelble, Hartmut, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKoch, Ursula E., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMieck, Ilja, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMieck, lija, eco